Cell.Text: [S] S|Yes, yes! Did Arch-Mage Aren send you? He sent you to rescue me, didn't he?
[S] What? The bo... Oh. Oh dear. | I shouldn't have taken them, I know! It was stupid. I was stupid. It won't happen again. | Help me get out of here, and I'll help you find them. Please!

Node.Caption: MG03OrthornHereforBooks: I'm just here for the books you took from the College.

Cell.Text: I don't have them anymore. She took them... The Caller. She's the one who put me in here! | Please, let me out of here!

Node.Caption: MG03OrthornStage50BranchTopic: Where are the books you stole?

Cell.Text: [S] S|Thank you, thank you! I promise I'll help. And then I'll go back to the College and I'll beg them to let me back in.
[S] S|Oh, you've saved me! Thank you so much. Who knows what they'd have done to me if you hadn't come along. | I promise I'll help you get out of here.
S|Ah. I see. | Well, then I'll just stay behind you a little bit, and follow along quietly.
[S] S|Yes, of course. I said I'd tell you, didn't I? | The Caller will have them. She was most interested in one of the volumes. | Although not interested enough to keep me from being locked up.

[S] S|The... the books? Oh, I see. I thought perhaps... Well, I thought you'd come for me. | But yes, the books. The Caller will have them. She was most interested in one of the volumes. | Although not interested enough to keep me from being locked up.
[S] See? I knew Aren wouldn't leave me in here! | Hurry and get me out of this cage before they come for me!

Node.Caption: MG03OrthornHereToRescue: I'm here to rescue you and recover the books you stole.

Cell.Text: They threw me in here until they were ready to use me in one of their experiments. | This wasn't supposed to happen. I thought they wanted my help, not to use me as a test subject!

Node.Caption: MG03Stage50OrthornWhyInCageTopic: Why are you in this cage?

Cell.Text: No, it's the levers in the center there. Just make sure you don't pull the wrong one. Please, hurry. I don't like being in here!

Node.Caption: MG03Stage50OrthornKeyTopic: Is there a key for this cage?
MG03OrthornStage55TakeAHikeTopic: You should get yourself to safety.

Cell.Text: [S] G|Well, I... If you're sure... | I'll just be on my way then. Please do be careful, and thank you.

Node.Caption: MG03OrthornStage55TakeAHikePolite: I can handle this on my own.

Cell.Text: [S] G|Well, I was only trying to help. | Fine, I'll just save myself then. Thank you for letting me out of that cage.

Node.Caption: MG03OrthornStage55TakeaHikeNotSoNice: This will be easier without you getting in my way.

Cell.Text: [S] G|I was only trying to help you, you know! | I hope the Caller turns you inside out!

Node.Caption: MG03OrthornStage55TakeAHikeMean: If you don't get away from me right now, I may kill you myself.
MG03OrthornStage55TakeAHikeNVM: You're right. I could use some help.
